Quote: Many years earlier [?c1890s] Mother had sent Don to the Post Office for a 2/6 postal note. Unfortunately she forgot to give him the poundage. `That's another penny, Sonny,' said the Postmaster cheerfully. With eyes flashing fire the small boy held up the PN.
